    "client_msg_id": "7024bae2-55af-4b8a-99fa-e3d499523b58",
    "text": "That said, I will definitely test this and I may end up using it. Not to replace the terminal, nor Emacs (my default command line interface), but as a way to integrate command line tools into browser workflows.",
